The inspection is already complete, so feel free to do as
you like.
It seems there are no traps in this area.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[11]What are you doing to such a small child!?

No matter what you say... I was merely measuring this
child's spiritual power!

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]Really, just that? You're not trying to do something
terrible to her?

I'm only doing the job I was told to do. What happens to
this child is none of my concern!

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Hello! I'm Amagawa Kohane! Right now, I'm the magical girl
Seraphier! And you are?
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Were you also kidnapped and brought here, Amy-chan?
It would be troublesome if I were seen...
Are you one of those Guardians' magical girls, big sister?
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Yes, that's right! I came here to defeat the kidnappers!
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Amy-chan, big sister will save you too!
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Yes! That's why I'm a magical girl!
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Amy-chan, let's get out of here together with big sister!
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Then let's head for the first floor! Let's go!
